00:17:24.319 --> 00:17:25.609
It's called Realizd.

00:17:25.609 --> 00:17:28.400
And Realizd has been
really insightful for me,

00:17:28.400 --> 00:17:31.100
and generates a lot of
aha moments for people

00:17:31.100 --> 00:17:32.110
I speak with as well.

00:17:32.110 --> 00:17:33.140
It's a free app.

00:17:33.140 --> 00:17:35.630
And what it does is it simply
tracks your phone usage

00:17:35.630 --> 00:17:36.920
in the back of your phone.

00:17:36.920 --> 00:17:39.295
Now your phone has ways that
you can do this on your own,

00:17:39.295 --> 00:17:40.730
whether Android or iPhone.

00:17:40.730 --> 00:17:44.090
But what I like about Realizd is
it gives a lot more statistics

00:17:44.090 --> 00:17:47.150
behind your usage of your phone,
including how many times you've

00:17:47.150 --> 00:17:48.890
picked it up, how
much time you've

00:17:48.890 --> 00:17:50.690
spent every time
you picked it up,

00:17:50.690 --> 00:17:53.390
what apps you were on for the
longest, what you were using,

00:17:53.390 --> 00:17:55.400
what your patterns
are over time.

00:17:55.400 --> 00:17:57.650
And it was most
eye opening to me

00:17:57.650 --> 00:17:59.290
when I was doing
research for my book.

00:17:59.290 --> 00:18:01.190
I'm going to be very
transparent with you.

00:18:01.190 --> 00:18:03.200
This is my real data right here.

00:18:03.200 --> 00:18:06.170
This is my real data during
