00:18:10.250 --> 00:18:12.600
there should be green if
you're in the good zone.

00:18:12.600 --> 00:18:14.700
They're yellow if you're
in a caution zone.

00:18:14.700 --> 00:18:17.290
And they're red if
you're not doing well.

00:18:17.290 --> 00:18:18.610
Red was my daughter's birthday.

00:18:18.610 --> 00:18:21.700
That's six hours on the
