with a lot of great hacks

00:20:24.720 --> 00:20:26.940
to make this a
little bit easier.

00:20:26.940 --> 00:20:29.550
I have a great friend in Dallas
whose name is Raj Daniels.

00:20:29.550 --> 00:20:32.830
He used to be CEO of a tech
startup called OpenTime.

00:20:32.830 --> 00:20:35.970
And he once created
this phone box screen

00:20:35.970 --> 00:20:37.560
